Description
	This program creates two threads which shares one variable(counter). The access of this shared variable is secured using Semaphore lock. Thread 2 would not access shared variable untill thread 1 finishes its execution.



Steps to compile
[1] make
	compiles program ThreadSync
[2] make clean
	clean up 

Output

 ./ThreadSync 
Thread 1 is now entering the thread function. 
Thread 2 is now entering the thread function. 
Thread 1 is now leaving the thread function. 
Value of counter is : 1
Thread 2 is now leaving the thread function. 
Value of counter is : 2

